# VEHICLE::GET_ENTITY_ATTACHED_TO_TOW_TRUCK

## Summary
Returns the entity index of the entity attached to this tow truck (-1 if is not attached)

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** towTruckVehicle

## Returns
* **ENTITY_INDEX**
